Posts.xml:217:  <row Id="225" PostTypeId="1" CreationDate="2010-09-03T18:00:40.583" Score="22" ViewCount="4765" Body="&lt;p&gt;This is the official site FAQ for Theoretical Computer Science. This question will contain a list of questions, with each question linking to a &lt;strong&gt;single&lt;/strong&gt; answer. If there is prior discussion on an answer, or you wish to discuss a particular answer, please create a separate meta question and link to it (so that this FAQ remains uncluttered). &lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The scope of this site:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://cstheory.meta.stackexchange.com/questions/225/official-faq-for-theoretical-computer-science/234#234&quot;&gt;Are questions about &lt;em&gt;[this area of computer science]&lt;/em&gt; on-topic here?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://cstheory.meta.stackexchange.com/questions/225/official-faq-for-theoretical-computer-science/235#235&quot;&gt;What kind of questions are too basic?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://cstheory.meta.stackexchange.com/questions/225/official-faq-for-theoretical-computer-science/238#238&quot;&gt;Specific questions about Theorem X in paper Y?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://cstheory.meta.stackexchange.com/questions/802/policy-questions-about-topic-for-research-project&quot;&gt;I'm looking for ideas for a project. Can I ask here ?&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://cstheory.meta.stackexchange.com/a/2661&quot;&gt;My question is not a research-level question in TCS, where can I ask it?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;How to use this site:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://cstheory.meta.stackexchange.com/questions/225/official-faq-for-theoretical-computer-science/232#232&quot;&gt;Can I discuss questions and answers on cstheory.sx?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ht